gobblin.config.store.api

Interface ConfigStoreWithBatchFetches

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ConfigStore

    @Alpha
public interface ConfigStoreWithBatchFetches
extends ConfigStore
    ConfigStoreWithBatchFetches indicate this ConfigStore support (efficient) fetching of batches of config keys with the same config version. For ConfigStore implementations that implement this interface, the config client library will delegate the batch fetches to the store instead of doing that itself. A typical use case for this interface is if the ConfigStore supports an RPC call which can fetch multiple config objects with a single call.
